                            <comment id="13266470" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 2 May 2012 10:08:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is that RangeStreamer excludes localhost by default, but it shouldn&apos;t do that for move.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached patch to fix (it moves the locahost exclusion out of RangeStreamer, but I think that is cleaner like that).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13266579" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 2 May 2012 14:16:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note: I&apos;ve also added a test for this in the dtests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
